id: REQ-fsm-bounded
kind: requirement
name: Mission state machine reaches a terminal state
status: draft
description: The mission state machine shall have exactly two terminal states: LANDED and RETURNING. Every non-terminal state shall have at least one transition that eventually leads to a terminal state. The system shall never deadlock in a non-terminal state indefinitely.
derives_from: NEED-safe-flight
verification_status: unverified
satisfied_by: BHV-mission-fsm
